s=\'mention\'><span class=\'mentions-prefix\'>@</span>yannickdecat</a> pela ajuda na redação e revisão deste post. Além disso, créditos a todos vocês que ajudaram a levar o Playground aonde ele está hoje!</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Fonte:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=E&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fmake.wordpress.org%2Fplayground%2F2025%2F12%2F03%2Fwordpress-playground-2025-year-in-review%2F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">WordPress Playground: 2025 Year in Review &#8211; Make WordPress</a></li>\n</ol>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"https://br.wordpress.org/2025/12/08/wordpress-playground-retrospectiva-de-2025/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"3371\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:4:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"WordPress 6.9 “Gene”\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://br.wordpress.org/2025/12/02/wordpress-6-9-gene/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";